{"tid":1147777,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有人不明　是想去私家醫院的　要不要規定去公營醫院服務才有分別","createTime":"2019-05-10T04:52:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T04:52:55.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6fd7c2c47799fdc5f2e6c2834c2b080b059d330f","tid":1147777,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T04:52:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10157094393507357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10157094393507357&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGt4mdtfFL54JHswKolAMfW8%3D&h=cf0e782f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10157094393507357</a><br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung:<br />\n今日又遇到有人唔明<br />\n本來就去公營醫院的，綁不綁公營醫院實習沒有分別。<br />\n是想去私家醫院的，要不要去公營醫院或部門實習才有分別，政府方案是方便人去私家，不是為解決公營醫院人手問題。<br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung:<br />\n而醫委會本來就是政府控制的，政府委任的委員佔了半數，呢場根本係政府做的大龍鳳。"}]}